tafsir[56]{c,v,t}:
  74,1,"Ko an yo mojoriiɗo comci mun (woni Annabiijo Muhammadu yo o his)."
  74,2,"Ɓaŋo renntinaa fii lepte Allah ɗen."
  74,3,"Mawninaa fii Joomi maa."
  74,4,"Laɓɓinaa hoore maa e junuubi, laɓɓintinoɗaa e soɓe."
  74,5,"Woɗɗito-ɗaa e rewugol sanamu."
  74,6,"Wata a okkiri fii Joomi maa ɓeydoraa ɗen golle maa ko ɓuri heewde."
  74,7,"Muññor fii Allah, e kala lorra ko heɓata maa."
  74,8,"Si wuttoyaama ɗiɗmun ka allaandu."
  74,9,"Haray ko nden woni ñalaande sattunde nden."
  74,10,"E hoore ɓen yedduɓe Allah e Nulaaɗo Makko on, nde wanaa newiinde."
  74,11,"An Nulaaɗo, accidam e mo Mi tagi on kañun tun, ka teege yumma makko, fewndo nde o alaano jawdi e ɓiɗɓe, on woni Waliid ibn al-Mughiirah."
  74,12,"Mi yeɗi mo jawdi ɗuuɗundi."
  74,13,"Mi waɗani mo ɓiɗɓe wonnduɓe e makko, tawdeteeɓe e makko tummbondire, ɓe seedataa e makko fii setagol, hakkee ko o ɗuuɗiraa jawdi."
  74,14,"Mi yaññani mo nguurndam e arsike e ɓiɗɓe, yaññudee."
  74,15,"Refti e hoore keeferaaku makko ngun, himo tamƴinoo nde mi ɓeydanta mo e hoore ɗum."
  74,16,"Wanaa no o sikkiri non ! Tawde o wonuno sanndalɗiiɗo e Aayeeje Amen jippinaaɗe e Nulaaɗo Amen on, o woni feenuɗo ɗe."
  74,17,"Aaray nde Mi fawata mo lette sattuɗe, ɗe o hattanoytaa ronnditagol."
  74,18,"O keefeero mbo neeminɗa ɗiin neemaali o miiliima ko o wiyata e Quraana ngam bonnude mbo, o hoddiri ɗuum e fittaandu makko."
  74,19,"O huɗaama o lepta hono no o hoddiri."
  74,20,"Refti o huɗa o lepta hono no o hoddiri."
  74,21,"Refti o ndaartandi ko o haalata."
  74,22,"Refti o ñirɓanii o ɓeydi ñirɓinaade, saanga nde o heɓaani ko o yuwri Quraana o."
  74,23,"Refti o runtii iimaan, o mawnikinii rewde e Annabi-yo o his-."
  74,24,"O wi*i: Ko Muhamadu addi ko, wonah haala Alla, kono ko ɗum mbilewu mbo o habrata ummaade woɓɓe."
  74,25,"Ko haala wonah haala Alla, kono ko ka haala aade."
  74,26,"Ma Mi naatnu o keefeero beɗi beɗi yiite, ngeen woni Saqara o muuse nguleeki henge."
  74,27,"Hol ko anndin Ma-aan muhamadu- ko woni yiite Saqara."
  74,28,"Nge heddatah hay huunde e leptateeɗe o singe arii e makko, nge accataa mbo haa o rutto no o laatarino nih, refti nge ara e makko kadi."
  74,29,"Sattunge sumgol e waylude guri."
  74,30,"Ina e dow mannge sappo e jeenay malayka, ko ɓeen ngoni reenooɓe nge."
  74,31,"Men waɗaali aynooɓe Yiite ngen, si wanaa Malaa'ikaaɓe, tawde neɗɗo waawaa ɗum. Abu Jahal fenuno fewndo o aaƴinoo wiide kanko e yimɓe makko ɓen ɓe waaway dartagol ɓen Malaa'ikaaɓe haa ɓe fuutoo e Yiite ngen. Hary non, Men waɗiraali limoore ɓen, si wanaa jarribagol yedduɓe Allah ɓen, fii no ɓe wowolira haala kan haala maɓɓe, lette ɗen sowanee ɓe, e fii no Alyaahuda yimɓe Tawreeta'en e Annasaara yimɓe Linnjiila'en fellitira fewndo jippagol Alqur'aana, wonnde ko nde goonginnde ko woni e Defte maɓɓe ɗen, e fii no gomɗimɓe ɓen ɓeydora gomɗinal tuma yimɓe Defte ɓen fottata e maɓɓe, e fii wata Alyahuuda e Annasaara e gomɗimɓe sikkito, e fii no murtuɓe e gomɗinal ɓen e heeferɓe ɓen wi'ira : hara ko honɗum Allah faandorii e ndee limooore haawniide? Ko wano ɓee yedduɓe ndee limoore majjinri non, goongimɓe ɓen feewiri ɗum, Allah majjinirta mo O muuyani majjugol, himo fewna kadi mo O muuyani feewugol. Hay gooto anndaa no koneeli Joomi maa ɗin fotata e ɗuuɗude, si wanaa Kanko tun. Yo Abu Jahal anndi ɗum, wi'unooɗo : Muhamaadu alaa wallooɓe si wanaa sappo e jeenay? O lamndori ɗum jalkitugol fenna. Haray ngen Yiite wonaali, si wanaa waaju wonannde neɗɗanke, fii ko o anndira mawngu Allah ngun."
  74,32,"Yo henane wanaa no yoga e sirkooɓe ɓen aaƴori non woniri, wonnde woɗɓe e maɓɓe waawanay halfinaaɓe Yiite ngen fii no ɓe fuutora. Allah woondirii lewru ndun."
  74,33,"O woondiri jemma si mbo runtiima."
  74,34,"O woondiri subaka si mbo jalbii."
  74,35,"Ko pellet, Yiite Jahannama ngen, ko jeyaange e musiibaaji mawɗi."
  74,36,"Ko nge jertinirnge e hulɓinirnge yimɓe ɓen."
  74,37,"Wonannde yiɗuɗo woo e mo'on onon yimɓe ɓen, nde o yaccotoo e gomɗingol Allah golla ko moƴƴi, maa o nennora keeferaaku e geddi."
  74,38,"Wonkii kala ko fagiikon e golle nanngirte, Ko si tawii golle makki halkay fii makki, maa si tawii hara ɗe daɗnday ki."
  74,39,"Si wanaa gomɗimɓe ɓen, ɓen ɗon nanngitiroytaake goopi mun, ɓe yawtanoyte ɗin, sabu golle maɓɓe moƴƴe ɗen."
  74,40,"Ɓe wonoyay Ñalnde Darngal e nder geese, hara hiɓe lamndondira hakkunde maɓɓe."
  74,41,"Fii heeferɓe halkirɓe ko'e mun ɓen golle geddi."
  74,42,"Ɓe wi'ana ɓen : ko honɗum naadi on Jahannama?"
  74,43,"Heeferɓe ɓen jaaboo ɓe : men jeyanooka e juulaynooɓe farlaaɗe ɗen e nguurndam aduna."
  74,44,"Men jeyanooka kadi e ñamminaynooɓe waasɓe ɓen e ko Allah yeɗi men kon."
  74,45,"Hari kadi ko yimɓe meere ɓen min yiiladaynoo e mun, men yewtida e majjuɓe bewɓe ɓen."
  74,46,"Hari kadi men fennayno fii ñalaande njoɓdi kuuɗe nden."
  74,47,"Men woni e fennugol ɗum, haa maayde nden arani men, men ronkii tuubude."
  74,48,"Nafataaɓe ñande darnga tefoore tefooɓe foti ko malayka wolla annabaaɓe e moƴƴuɓe, sabu ina e sarteeli tefngo weluya tefanteeɗo."
  74,49,"Honde huunde taki ɓe sirkuɓe na ɗuurnoo Quraana?"
  74,50,"Hoɓe mba*i e ɗuurnagol mum en e dokgol mum en e bamɗi ladde cattuɗi dokgol."
  74,51,"Dokɗi mbaroodi ngam hulde ndi."
  74,52,"Gooto e sirkuɓe na faala nde wonata e hoore makko deftere saraande hollre wonde Muhamadu ko nelaaɓɗo ummaade ka Alla, ɗum noon sababu mum wonah famɗude daliil wollo lohde ɗi, kono tagi ɗum ko sanndalinde e mawnikinaade."
  74,53,"Huunde nde wonah hono noon, woni sabaabu doonaade ɓe e majjere mum en ko ɓe goonɗinaani lepte laakara, ɓe keddii e keeferaagal mum en."
  74,54,"Pellet Quraana ko waaju e siftanirde"
  74,55,"Kala faalaaɗo nde o janngata Quraana o waactaroo mbo, o jannga mbo o waactaroo mbo."
  74,56,"ɓe mbaactataako si wonah tawi ko Alla faala nde ɓe mbaactato, ko Kanko ceniiɗo O haandi e hulireede siinude jamirooje Mum e reentaaade kaɗaaɗe Makko, Hombo haandi e yaafaade maccuɓe Makko si ɓe tuubi."
